snippet.title: Diana and Roma Fun weekend with Parents at Ferrari World theme park in Abu Dhabi
snippet.description:
Over the weekend, Diana and Roma and their parents visited the superb Ferrari World theme park in Abu Dhabi. The children spent the whole day with their parents, riding the rides. It was an unforgettable day of adventure!
Thanks for watching!
